### Admin diagnostics
### Requires: {{baseUrl}} and {{accessToken}} in http-client env

### whoami — returns the caller's sub/username/email/groups/role plus a
### diagnostic.missingGroupsLikelyPreTokenGen flag the frontend uses to
### render the AuthHealthBanner. If groups is empty AND tokenUse is
### "access", the Pre Token Generation Lambda is broken or unwired —
### see backend/cognito-pre-token-gen/README.md.
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/whoami
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Same call without auth — should return 401 from API Gateway authorizer.
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/whoami

###
